Zaka East Member of Parliament Samson Mukanduri has died. Zanu PF party officials in Masvingo said Mukanduri was found dead at his rural home in Chiromo village after complaining of high blood pressure. BY STAFF REPORTER Zaka Central MP Paradzai Chakona confirmed the death. “It’s a sad day for the people of Zaka district and Masvingo at large. His death has come as a shock to us and he will be greatly missed,” Chakona said. Mukanduri had been Zaka East MP since 2008.